OL,3,CWhich councils are expected to
OL,4,Cpostpone their local elections in May?
OL,6,FBy Senior Politics Producers Lili
OL,7,FDonlon-Mansbridge and Elisa Menendez
OL,9,FMore than a third of councils in
OL,10,FEngland have asked to postpone their
OL,11,Flocal elections in May as part of a
OL,12,Fmajor shake-up to local government.
OL,14,FA total of 27 local authorities have
OL,15,Fasked to push back their ballots or
OL,16,Fare still considering doing so, with
OL,17,F19 of them being councils run by
OL,18,FLabour, ITV News understands.
