OL,3,CWhich councils are expected to
OL,4,Cpostpone their local elections in May?
OL,6,FSome elections were delayed last year
OL,7,Funtil May 2026 as part of Labour's
OL,8,Foverhaul to local government. However,
OL,9,Fthe government announced before
OL,10,FChristmas that some elections may be
OL,11,Fdelayed yet again, pushing them to
OL,12,F2027.
OL,14,FMinisters are planning to abolish the
OL,15,Ftwo-tier system of district and county
OL,16,Fcouncils in the hopes of making the
OL,17,Fsystem more streamlined and offering
OL,18,Fbetter services to voters.
