OL,3,CWhich councils are expected to
OL,4,Cpostpone their local elections in May?
OL,6,FLast month, ministers wrote to 63
OL,7,Fcouncils that were scheduled to hold
OL,8,Felections in May, offering the option
OL,9,Fto push them back because the
OL,10,Frestructure is taking longer than
OL,11,Fexpected.
OL,13,FMinisters informed the selected
OL,14,Fcouncils they would authorise the
OL,15,Fdelays if there were "genuine
OL,16,Fconcerns" about the ability to deliver
OL,17,Felections alongside the restructuring
OL,18,Fplans.
