OL,3,CWhich councils are expected to
OL,4,Cpostpone their local elections in May?
OL,6,FLabour has sparked backlash for the
OL,7,Fmove with opposition critics accusing
OL,8,Fthem of "running scared" of voters, at
OL,9,Fa time when the party is doing badly
OL,10,Fin the polls, and smaller parties such
OL,11,Fas Reform UK and the Green Party are
OL,12,Fsurging.
OL,14,FThe majority seeking a postponement
OL,15,Fare Labour councils, however there are
OL,16,Fthree Tory and two Lib Dem ones also
OL,17,Fconsidering it, while others are of no
OL,18,Foverall control.
