OL,3,CWhich councils are expected to
OL,4,Cpostpone their local elections in May?
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer earlier argued that
OL,7,Fhis government is introducing the
OL,8,F"biggest reorganisation of councils
OL,9,Ffor 50 years" and that it is "only
OL,10,Fright" to ask "whether it makes sense
OL,11,Fto elect people to positions when the
OL,12,Fcouncil itself is going to change in a
OL,13,Fvery short period of time."
OL,15,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting also
OL,16,Fdefended the decision and pointed out
OL,17,Fthat councils from a range of
OL,18,Fpolitical parties are planning to
OL,19,Fdelay.
