OL,4,Cpostpone their local elections in May?
OL,6,FShadow local government secretary Sir
OL,7,FJames Cleverly accused Labour of
OL,8,F"running scared of voters because they
OL,9,Fknow they are set for a ballot-box
OL,10,Fbattering due to their disastrous
OL,11,Fperformance in office".
OL,13,F"This government is denying democracy
OL,14,Fand depriving local communities of the
OL,15,Fright to choose who represents them.
OL,16,FAs a result, some councillors will now
OL,17,Fend up serving a seven-year term," he
OL,18,Fadded.
